---
import Layout from '@layouts/Layout.astro';
import Container from '@components/container.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy - Infinite Limit, LLC">
  <Container>
    <section class="py-16">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Privacy Policy for Infinite Limit, LLC</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4"><strong>Effective Date:</strong> February 26, 2025</p>

      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6">
        Hi there! At Infinite Limit, LLC, we value your privacy. This policy explains what happens with your info when you use our website, which is pretty simple since we just have a contact form.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-3">What We Collect</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">When you use our contact form, we collect:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-10 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li>Your name, email, and message (whatever you type in).</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">That’s it—no cookies, no tracking, just the basics to get back to you.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-3">How We Use It</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">We use your info to:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-10 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li>Reply to your message.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        That’s all! Our contact form is powered by Web3Forms, which sends your details straight to our email and doesn’t keep it hanging around.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-3">Who We Share It With</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-2">We don’t sell or share your info, except:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-10 text-gray-600 mb-4">
        <li>
          Web3Forms processes it briefly to deliver your message to us (check 
          <a href="https://web3forms.com/privacy" target="_blank" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">their privacy policy</a> 
          for details).
        </li>
        <li>If the law asks us to share it (super unlikely).</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-3">Your Choices</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Want your info gone? Just ask us to delete your message after we’ve responded—easy peasy.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-3">How We Keep It Safe</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        We rely on Web3Forms’ security to handle your form data, and once it’s in our email, we protect it with standard measures like passwords. No system’s perfect, but we’ve got your back.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-800 mt-6 mb-3">Contact Us</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">
        Questions? Please contact us at <a href="mailto:p.oflaherty@infinitelimit.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">p.oflaherty@infinitelimit.com</a>.
      </p>

      <p class="text-gray-600">
        We’ll update this if anything changes. Thanks for stopping by!
      </p>
    </section>
  </Container>
</Layout>